content: RT @realDonaldTrumpMark Levin: “Here she (Kamala Harris) is basically comparing U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement's (ICE), to the perception of the Ku Klux Klan…the combination of stupidity and arrogance is on full display, right here!”
